docs.snippet: BUENOS AIRES, Jan. 26 (AP).-- Argentina captured two firsts tonight in the finals of the three-day Pan-American swimming meet to give the host team victory over the United States, Ecuador, Uruguay and Chile.
docs.lead_paragraph: BUENOS AIRES, Jan. 26 (AP).-- Argentina captured two firsts tonight in the finals of the three-day Pan-American swimming meet to give the host team victory over the United States, Ecuador, Uruguay and Chile.

headline.main: ARGENTINE SWIMMERS DEFEAT U.S. IN MEET; Ecuador Third at Buenos Aires --Three Americans Ill

docs.lead_paragraph: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, Jan. 26.--The Finance Ministers of Argentina, Brazil, Paraguay and Uruguay will meet here tomorrow for a three-day conference at which they hope to work out a basis for a new international commercial and fiscal policy among their countries.

docs.snippet: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, Jan. 28.--Two important conferences will meet here next week to study the many complicated juridical, technical and sanitary problems that have arisen as a result of the rapid growth of aerial navigation in the Americas.
